  "id": "sCLpVb4V",
  "slug": "craft-stairs-back-into-blocks",
  "title": "Craft Stairs Back Into Blocks",
  "description": "Automatically generates recipes for crafting blocks from stairs",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wishful-recipes\"><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/91/a0/caG03Acz_o.png\" alt=\"This mod has been made part of Wishful Recipes. Please check it out by clicking on this. It can dynamically generate recipes on its own, meaning it is highly compatible with other mods and requires less configuration. \"/></a>\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eTU355T.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/craft-stairs-back-into-blocks\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1305885?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/craft-stairs-back-into-blocks\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/craft-stairs-back-into-blocks?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">With this fully automated and configurable mod, you can craft stairs back into full blocks. Allowing you to recycle stairs you no longer need. These recipes can be generated automatically by scanning for stair shape recipes, or you can configure them yourself. Thanks to the automatic scanning, the mod is highly compatible with other mods that add new types of stairs, requiring no manual setup.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QsMZSIL.png\"/></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/betterstairscrafting.json</code> in your profile folder. Please note that any changes will require restarting Minecraft to take effect.</p>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>block_amount</b> - determines how many blocks you get from crafting</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>add_recipes_manually</b> - if set to true, this mod stops generating these recipes automatically and generates them based on the list bellow</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>block_stairs_list</b> - list of stairs and the corresponding blocks you craft from them</p></center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>",
